imdb.plot outline: Better Homes and Onions is a comedy web series that parodies trending lifestyle programs, providing extraordinary and 'out of this world' home living strategies, all of which involve one magic ingredient: Onions. The three stars and home living gurus are Willy; the ego inflated personal trainer; Ollie, the disabled award winning chef; and Sheila, the ill fated and hopelessly bitter host. The series reveals the dichotomy between what the viewer sees and the outrageous and unseemly truth of reality TV stars.
